{"tid":138038,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[歷史上的如果]如果當年中國加入左軸心國","createTime":"2017-02-28T09:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T16:37:04.000Z","uid":1355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"25cbca874569c7a5cec8017eba4296924b0660af","tid":138038,"uid":1355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T09:54:01.000Z","msg":"如果當年中國加入軸心國，聯同日本一齊攻打蘇聯。巴巴羅沙作戰會唔會成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d0b6aad5bb07168d1149870c1f720785dd28935","tid":138038,"uid":45941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T09:55:50.000Z","msg":"但日本唔會想同中國一隊吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n始終佢想食左中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4626da1170f5ed81fe9b10b57fd3ca29dd860e3b","tid":138038,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T09:57:33.000Z","msg":"國軍d裝備冇可能應付到西伯利亞環境<br />\n又冇裝甲師<br />\n<br />\n可能會拖埋大日本帝國後腿"},{"pid":"9e225f579e6ef7ef89f4202746f6e5fea24bb096","tid":138038,"uid":1355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T09:58:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但日本唔會想同中國一隊吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n始終佢想食左中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打完蘇聯先打中國，好似德蘇入侵波蘭之後簽和約咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a195ee97a225c15d8ab0d9f27438e3a67bc38fb2","tid":138038,"uid":1355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T09:59:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國軍d裝備冇可能應付到西伯利亞環境<br />\n又冇裝甲師<br />\n<br />\n可能會拖埋大日本帝國後腿</blockquote><br />\n成為另一個意大利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b0779ffe790d749ffa20cc34fa9979cb9bc8b4","tid":138038,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T10:04:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但日本唔會想同中國一隊吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n始終佢想食左中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未必，日本要的是中國資源，例如佢會承認汪精衛政權<br />\n<br />\n如果汪氏路線為國民黨其他大佬接受，國民政府咪加入軸心<br />\n但對大局無影響，因為其時中國不產油，日本一樣會打南洋，<br />\n一樣要挑戰美國<br />\n<br />\n真係可能加入軸心又有大影響既係蘇聯<br />\n不過德日都反共，接受唔到蘇聯加入"},{"pid":"92b1081792bcc11f4c19e7ecdb3274d4bcdda5db","tid":138038,"uid":72446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T11:38:05.000Z","msg":"邊有可能<br />\n就好似德國想用蘇聯做生產咁，點會同你同盟<br />\n<br />\n如果中國得，東南亞都得架，打咩?"},{"pid":"45aec7bb3c9f7a348bf114206be89b0319e6c021","tid":138038,"uid":39871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T11:40:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>國軍d裝備冇可能應付到西伯利亞環境<br />\n又冇裝甲師<br />\n<br />\n可能會拖埋大日本帝國後腿</blockquote><br />\n成為另一個意大利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n軍事上, 恐怕中國無能力成為第二個意大利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過咁, 中國資源豐富(自然,人力)<br />\n拖後腿又未必既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f3ee16f7fe8c7e9ca2f41c1e0707c012b76544","tid":138038,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T11:52:55.000Z","msg":"意大利唔會再比人笑"},{"pid":"f8c94fbca899e267fe7b8223a432d80c71f0f419","tid":138038,"uid":33213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:22:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊有可能<br />\n就好似德國想用蘇聯做生產咁，點會同你同盟<br />\n<br />\n如果中國得，東南亞都得架，打咩?</blockquote><br />\n其實德國都唔係冇諗過同中國結盟<br />\n話曬咁多資源<br />\n只係軍工爛泥扶唔上壁先揀日本<br />\n<br />\n同埋最後日本都走數冇打蘇聯<br />\n畀人打就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148efc918d0f5b609e1d45389b72f17d25c47276","tid":138038,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:56:45.000Z","msg":"中國加入軸心國, 日本一樣打鳩中國<br />\n<br />\n日本最多自己自成一國, 唔加入任何同盟"},{"pid":"be099a18bb5487f5389cc22d9018ca86e6c56a4d","tid":138038,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:58:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國加入軸心國, 日本一樣打鳩中國<br />\n<br />\n日本最多自己自成一國, 唔加入任何同盟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n事實上, 係二戰到<br />\n日本一直孤軍作戰<br />\n<br />\n反而德國最起碼有意大利, 匈牙利, 羅馬尼亞 ,保加利亞, 呢D國家做盟友<br />\n德國同日本雖然是盟友,但大家相距太遠, 戰場又唔同, 完全無乜互動"},{"pid":"5f3c051d0f57bdec9a63b68c628c5a715a5bf7b9","tid":138038,"uid":3500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:58:15.000Z","msg":"連德國都攻唔入USSR <br />\n你估中國人多就可以攻得入咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf00a02105b96f62b438e8e2456d11557e77c1f4","tid":138038,"uid":19542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:00:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連德國都攻唔入USSR <br />\n你估中國人多就可以攻得入咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你試下同佢地講食俄佬會補身 俄佬一日就滅族"},{"pid":"3c2344f6291a772fd69b6f2f7e059c5c55a66abc","tid":138038,"uid":1355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:15:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊有可能<br />\n就好似德國想用蘇聯做生產咁，點會同你同盟<br />\n<br />\n如果中國得，東南亞都得架，打咩?</blockquote><br />\n其實德國都唔係冇諗過同中國結盟<br />\n話曬咁多資源<br />\n只係軍工爛泥扶唔上壁先揀日本<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同埋最後日本都走數冇打蘇聯</span><br />\n畀人打就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇記錯關東軍俾蘇聯打到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  如果靠德國輸出技術，將中國變成兵工廠又有冇可能呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b0ac9f90720aaaf0dcf58acb6839a1681a52566","tid":138038,"uid":65770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:38:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國軍d裝備冇可能應付到西伯利亞環境<br />\n又冇裝甲師<br />\n<br />\n可能會拖埋大日本帝國後腿</blockquote><br />\n希特拉調停918事變主要想形成包圍共產主義圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55d44b7567d38cce779c6bee17ada2f50144bec","tid":138038,"uid":1355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:39:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>國軍d裝備冇可能應付到西伯利亞環境<br />\n又冇裝甲師<br />\n<br />\n可能會拖埋大日本帝國後腿</blockquote><br />\n希特拉調停918事變主要想形成包圍共產主義圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但結果雙方都唔肯收手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7aff40cb8c2a86878f6636778a6423e21cae79","tid":138038,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:55:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>國軍d裝備冇可能應付到西伯利亞環境<br />\n又冇裝甲師<br />\n<br />\n可能會拖埋大日本帝國後腿</blockquote><br />\n希特拉調停918事變主要想形成包圍共產主義圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但結果雙方都唔肯收手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n民國已經比共產黨完全滲透，最後做埋蘇聯人肉盾牌"},{"pid":"b6b5e3fe8237c07bbe8cb589b79c269cfd929a03","tid":138038,"uid":15063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:10:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連德國都攻唔入USSR <br />\n你估中國人多就可以攻得入咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你試下同佢地講食俄佬會補身 俄佬一日就滅族</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個post 本身好認真， 而家比你破壞晒"},{"pid":"5bfa3368ca3e0b3500c38db74183c539110e83f7","tid":138038,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:10:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>國軍d裝備冇可能應付到西伯利亞環境<br />\n又冇裝甲師<br />\n<br />\n可能會拖埋大日本帝國後腿</blockquote><br />\n希特拉調停918事變主要想形成包圍共產主義圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1931年 希特拉調停918事變<br />\n1933年 希特拉政府上台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba21db050